            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/19",
              "text": "أَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام )"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ],
          "text": "عَلِيُّ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ عَنْ أَبِيهِ عَنِ ابْنِ أَبِي عُمَيْرٍ عَنْ هِشَامِ بْنِ سَالِمٍ عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) قَالَ"
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/al-kafi:5:2:11:1",
        "text": [
          " كَانَ أَمِيرُ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ صَلَوَاتُ اللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ يَحْتَطِبُ وَ يَسْتَقِي وَ يَكْنُسُ وَ كَانَتْ فَاطِمَةُ سَلَامُ اللَّهِ عَلَيْهَا تَطْحَنُ وَ تَعْجِنُ وَ تَخْبِزُ ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hisham Bin Salim, ",
            "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> used to ignite the fire and draw the water and sweep, and Syed Fatima<sup>asws</sup> used to grind and knead and bake’."
          ],
          "en.sarwar": [
            "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hisham ibn Salim abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, who has said the following: “Amir al-Mu’minin, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, would bring firewood, water and sweep the house. Fatimah al- Zahra’, ‘Alayha al-Salam, would grind wheat, make dough and bake.” "
          ]
        }
